AD.1.5.12.5 Network Settings	/etc/sysctl.conf

"La equivalencia en Linux es:
"En /etc/sysctl.conf:
"# Disables packet forwarding
"net.ipv4.ip_forward = 0

/sbin/sysctl -a |grep -i net.ipv4.ip_forward
